data.title: McKendree University Names Students to its Spring 2024 President’s, Dean’s Lists
data.meta_description: McKendree University congratulates the 193 students who were named to its President’s List and the 340 students who made the Dean’s List for the spring semester.
data.text:
(LEBANON, Ill., June 12, 2024) – McKendree University congratulates the 193 students who were named to its President’s List and the 340 students who made the Dean’s List for the spring semester. These students exhibited an exceptional academic performance during the spring 2024 semester. To be named to the President’s List, a student must earn a perfect 4.0 grade point average for the term. The Dean’s List requires a grade point average of 3.60 or higher.
